descript.abstract: This polygon data layer represents zoning for the City of Madison, Wisconsin in 2014. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Madison_City_Zoning_2014.gdb. [City of Madison Wisconsin Zoning Districts http://www.cityofmadison.com/dpced/]
descript.purpose: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data. [This feature is used by the City of Madison Department of Planning and Community & Economic, Development to determine zoning for the entire city.]
